summary:
Summary of New Email Messages:

1. **Subject**: Overdue: Operating system update will install today
   - **Sender**: Rippling <no-reply@rippling.com>
   - **Snippet**: Notification about an automatic operating system update scheduled for today as part of IT security policy. The user is advised to update their computer before enforcement to avoid any issues.
   - **Urgency**: High, due to the immediate action required to update the operating system.

2. **Subject**: Nathan, time to jump back into your Weights & Biases certification!
   - **Sender**: "W&B AI Academy" <noreply@notify.thinkific.com>
   - **Snippet**: Encouragement for Nathan to continue his progress on the Weights & Biases course, which is 21% complete.
   - **Urgency**: Low, as this is a motivational reminder rather than an urgent task.
